item.title: An Introduction
item.description: Last September or so, I applied at the local community college, and I was so excited. I had been working outside on my traffic control job for at least over a year at this point, and I wasn’t at all looking forward to working in the winter. And yet, when the quarter started and the going started getting toughâ€¦ I folded. I stopped turning in homework, and I dropped my math and english class, leaving only my college success class.
